<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Time de Vôlei</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-image: url('https://source.unsplash.com/1600x900/?volleyball');
            background-size: cover;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            background-position: center;
            color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
            background-color: #9b6f36
        }

        header {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background: #000000cc;
            padding: 20px;
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .logo-container img {
            height: 50px;
        }

        .logo-text {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background: #d9a94f;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            background: #c9732c;
        }

        .main-container {
            padding: 50px 20px 40px;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 100px auto;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <div class="logo-container">
            <img src="/fotos/Wiki_logo2(1)(1).png" alt="Logo Time de Vôlei">
            <div class="logo-text">WikiOsasco - Sistema Administrativo</div>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/admin/Jogo/lst">Jogos</a></li>
                <li><a href="/admin/escalacao/lst">Escalação</a></li>
                <li><a href="/admin/socio/lst">Sócios</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="main-container">
        <h1>Bem-vindo ao Sistema Administrativo do Time</h1>
        <p>Utilize o menu acima para navegar entre as seções de jogos, escalação e sócios.</p>
    </div>

</body>

</html>
